---
const problems = [
  {
    title: "Unclear offer",
    copy: "Visitors should understand what you sell, who it helps, and why it matters within seconds.",
    icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path>`
  },
  {
    title: "Messy course experience",
    copy: "A course needs clear modules, lessons, downloads, progress flow, and student navigation.",
    icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path>`
  },
  {
    title: "Weak launch system",
    copy: "Your pages, checkout, email follow-up, and student access should feel connected.",
    icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>`
  }
];
---
<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-6">Your Kajabi site should not feel unfinished, generic, or confusing</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-textMuted leading-relaxed">
        Many course creators have strong expertise, but their Kajabi setup does not clearly show the offer, organize the learning experience, or guide visitors toward enrollment. TheEduAssist helps clean up the full journey from website and landing pages to course structure, funnels, emails, and launch flow.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {problems.map((item) => (
        <div class="bg-brand-softBg border border-brand-border rounded-2xl p-8 hover-lift hover:border-brand-accent/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center text-brand-accent mb-6 border border-brand-border">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" set:html={item.icon}></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">{item.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-textMuted leading-relaxed">{item.copy}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
